question: how high is the share of people living in proximity of a busstop in Bauma (bis 2014)?
sql:
select iv.value from indicator_values2 iv
join indicators i on iv.indicator_id = i.indicator_id
join spatialunit s on iv.spatialunit_id = s.spatialunit_id
where i.name like 'Access by bus [% of inhabitants]' and s.name like 'Bauma (bis 2014)'

question: How many municipalities have a share of people living in proximity of a busstop higher than 90.1 per year?
sql:
select iv.year, count(*) from
indicator_values2 iv
join indicators i on iv.indicator_id = i.indicator_id
join spatialunit s on iv.spatialunit_id = s.spatialunit_id
where iv.VALUE > 90.1 and s.type_id = 1 and i.name like 'Access by bus [% of inhabitants]' group by iv.year
